h || \u2013\n|-\n! [[2020 MotoGP season|2020]]\n| MotoGP\n| [[Yamaha YZR-M1]]\n| [[Yamaha Motor Racing|Monster Energy Yamaha MotoGP]]\n| 46\n| - || - || - || - || - || - || - || \u2013\n|-\n! colspan=5| Total\n| '''402'''\n| '''115'''\n| '''234'''\n| '''65'''\n| '''96'''\n| '''6247'''\n|\n| '''9'''\n|}\n\n====By class====\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:right;\"\n|-\n!Class\n!Seasons\n!1st GP\n!1st Pod\n!1st Win\n!Race\n!Win\n!Podiums\n![[Pole position|Pole]]\n!FLap\n!Pts\n!WChmp\n|-\n! 125cc\n| 1996\u20131997\n| align=\"left\"| [[1996 Malaysian motorcycle Grand Prix|1996 Malaysia]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[1996 Austrian motorcycle Grand Prix|1996 Austria]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[1996 Czech Republic motorcycle Grand Prix|1996 Czech Republic]]\n| 30 || 12 || 15 || 5 || 9 || 432 || 1\n|-\n! 250cc\n| 1998\u20131999\n| align=\"left\"| [[1998 Japanese motorcycle Grand Prix|1998 Japan]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[1998 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|1998 Spain]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[1998 Dutch TT|1998 Netherlands]]\n| 30 || 14 || 21 || 5 || 11 || 510 || 1\n|-\n! 500cc\n| 2000\u20132001\n| align=\"left\"| [[2000 South African motorcycle Grand Prix|2000 South Africa]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[2000 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2000 Spain]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[2000 British motorcycle Grand Prix|2000 Great Britain]]\n| 32 || 13 || 23 || 4 || 15 || 534 || 1\n|-\n! MotoGP\n| 2002\u2013present\n| align=\"left\"| [[2002 Japanese motorcycle Grand Prix|2002 Japan]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[2002 Japanese motorcycle Grand Prix|2002 Japan]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[2002 Japanese motorcycle Grand Prix|2002 Japan]]\n| 310 || 76 || 175 || 51 || 61 || 4771 || 6\n|-\n! Total\n! colspan=4|1996\u2013Present\n| '''402'''\n| '''115'''\n| '''234'''\n| '''65'''\n| '''96'''\n| '''6247'''\n| '''9'''\n|}\n\n====Races by year====\n([[Template:Motorsport driver results legend|key]]) (Races in '''bold''' indicate pole position, races in ''italics'' indicate fastest lap)\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=