ustria]], [[Czech Republic]], [[Brazil]], [[Australia]], [[Argentina]], [[South Africa]], [[Portugal]], [[Qatar]], [[China]], [[United States]], [[Turkey]], [[Thailand]]){{Citation needed|date=October 2018}}\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:left;\"| Wins at [[Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya]]\n| 10 ([[1997 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|1997]]\u2013[[1999 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|1999]], [[2001 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2001]]\u2013[[2002 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2002]], [[2004 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2004]]\u2013[[2006 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2006]], [[2009 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2009]], [[2016 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2016]])\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:left;\"| Wins at [[Mugello Circuit]]\n| 9 ([[1997 Italian motorcycle Grand Prix|1997]], [[1999 Italian motorcycle Grand Prix|1999]], [[2002 Italian motorcycle Grand Prix|2002]]\u2013[[2008 Italian motorcycle Grand Prix|2008]])\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:left;\"| Wins at [[Circuito de Jerez-\u00c1ngel Nieto]]\n| 9 ([[1997 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|1997]], [[1999 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|1999]], [[2001 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2001]]\u2013[[2003 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2003]], [[2005 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2005]], [[2007 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2007]], [[2009 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2009]], [[2016 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix|2016]])\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:left;\"| Wins at [[Phillip Island Grand Prix Circuit]]\n| 8 ([[1998 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|1998]]\u2013[[1999 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|1999]], [[2001 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|2001]]\u2013[[2005 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|2005]], [[2014 Australian motorcycle Grand Prix|2014]])\n|-\n!style=\"text-align:left;\"| Wins at [[Donington Park]]\n| 7 ([[1997 British motorcycle Grand Prix|1997]], [[1999 British motorcycle Grand Prix|1999]]\u2013[[2002 British motorcycle Grand Prix|2002]], [[2004 British motorcycle Grand Prix|2004]]\u2013[[2005 British motorcycle Grand Prix|2005]])